column1: # Notes:This file includes starting and ending ranges for feature = "gene" in the gtf file.
#   chr character chromosome in genome build GRCh37/hg19
#   gene_id character gene identifier with ENSG prefix
#   agg_start integer 5' start position of the feature in genome build GRCh37/hg19
#   agg_end integer 3' end position of the gene in genome build GRCh37/hg19
#   source comma seprated list annotation sources of transcripts in an aggregation unit
#   type character biotype of the feature
#   merge_count integer number of features joined in aggregation unit
#   agg_size integer length of aggregation unit
